OL,5, A Scottish government minister racked  
OL,6, up nearly #11,000 in roaming costs on  
OL,7, his parliament iPad while in Morocco.  
OL,9,FMichael Matheson said he was using the 
OL,10,Fdevice for constituency work, but had  
OL,11,Fnot switched over to the parliament's  
OL,12,Fcurrent mobile contract.               
